stions/1","/blocks/8/content/questions/2"],"excerpt":"How many solid dots must be visible... How many total 'tails' are shown...","problem":"These questions prioritize basic arithmetic and counting over technical reasoning or symbol identification.","whyItMatters":"Numeric 'counting' questions do not confirm if the student understands the electrical function of the symbol, only that they can count marks on a diagram.","alignmentGap":"GENERAL PEDAGOGY"}]},"sessionId":"generation"}
